Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,, Sakamoto Čino \N Šimazaki Wakako
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,, Gotó Šódžiró \N Munetaka Aoki
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwasaki Kisei \N Maiko
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakamoto Haru \N Acuko Maeda
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,, Sató Jonosuke \N Arizono Jošiki
